title: Inspired Collective Dance Ensemble  Presents: Doll House
desc:
Inspired Collective Presents: Doll House? 
 ? Join us in a night of music and dance performance as Inspired Collective Dance Ensemble makes their stage debut. Inspired Collective Dance Ensemble empowers youth to cultivate their talent and passion for the performing arts to further excel in life. Inspired Collective Dance Ensemble is made up of aspiring young artist and leaders who seek to uplift and enlighten our community through leadership and dance. Support us as we continue to uplift a generation through the performing arts.? 
 ?Ballet, jazz, modern and african complete the? prism that is? Isabella?s Doll House, where things may not be as perfect as they seem..... 
 
 NOTE: There are two different show times. The student ticket includes youth 17 years old and under. Lap children (who don't need a seat) 4 years old and under are free.?Limited amount of tickets will be sold at the door. 
 Can't make the show? Feel free to make a donation!
